>
<br>
I cast it and then sit down.  That way I don't move my character around, just the eye, plus I mediate while scouting around.  <br>
<br>
Don't know what is behind the door, send in the eye.  Looks like 3 mobs.  Target one, send in the pet.  Opps ten more aggro, time to gate.  You can order your pet to go places you can't see normally.  Then you can see what happens from a safe distance.  <br>
<br>
With this spell, you should never be surprised by what is in a room again.  {Unless the door is locked}.  <br>
